      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-omega closure selected based on published benchmark performance for centrifugal pump flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model applied with literature-validated coefficients. Model form assessed as adequate for nominal operating conditions. No model form assessment performed for fault-induced flow regimes such as impeller imbalance vibration or intermittent cavitation from bearing wear."
