    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD model demonstrates hemolysis index predictions within 8% of experimental benchmark across all 5 COU operating points. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all nominal operating conditions. The validation campaign is judged sufficient to support the tolerance-sensitivity decision for the Class II CPB device.",
